<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 2 (Milla) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ミラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Milla</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ジュード</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Jude</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>今度から機械の扱いには気をつけよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll be more careful when dealing
with machinery from now on.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いきなり斬ったりしたらだめだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You can't just go around
suddenly slashing them like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>機械細工に防御力を期待してはいけない。
そういう事なのだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So I can't expect defensive measures
from machinery. So that's how it is.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん。
期待してたのはミラだけだと思うよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right. I think you're the only one
who had any other expectations.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうなのか？
難しいものだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that right?
These things sure are difficult to figure out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
